<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://blog.avritek.com/2016/01/21/operation-black-atlas-new-botnet-accessing-pos-systems-via-windows-update/">POS Systems Botnet vulnerability? Recycle and destroy obsolete machines.</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://blog.avritek.com">Avritek Blog | Secure Technology Asset Solutions</a>.</p>
]]></content>
