<p><a href="http://searchsolidstatestorage.techtarget.com/definition/single-level-cell-SLC-flash"><span style="font-weight: 400;">http://searchsolidstatestorage.techtarget.com/definition/single-level-cell-SLC-flash</span></a></p>
