		<title type="html"><![CDATA[AVR Recycling is now Avritek!]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://blog.avritek.com/2015/10/28/avr-recycling-is-now-avritek/" />
		<id>http://blog.avritek.com/?p=1357</id>
		<updated>2015-11-02T17:15:16Z</updated>
		<published>2015-10-28T15:44:47Z</published>
		<category scheme="http://blog.avritek.com" term="Uncategorized" />		<summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I am thrilled to announce that AVR Recycling is now Avritek!   As our business has evolved we wanted to ensure that our brand was truly reflective of the services we provide our clients. &#160; While we will continue to provide the same electronic recycling services we have always offered our clients, our services have evolved to be even more focused [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://blog.avritek.com/2015/10/28/avr-recycling-is-now-avritek/">AVR Recycling is now Avritek!</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://blog.avritek.com">Avritek Blog | Secure Technology Asset Solutions</a>.</p>
]]></summary>
		<content type="html" xml:base="http://blog.avritek.com/2015/10/28/avr-recycling-is-now-avritek/"><![CDATA[<div><span style="color: #202020;">I am thrilled to announce that <span class="il">AVR</span> Recycling is now<a href="http://www.avritek.com"> </a></span><a href="http://www.avritek.com"><span class="il">Avritek</span>!</a><span style="color: #202020;"><a href="http://www.avritek.com"> </a>  As our business has evolved we wanted </span><span style="color: #000000;">to ensure</span><span style="color: #202020;"> that our brand was truly reflective of the services we provide our clients.</span></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div>
<div>
<div>While we will continue to provide the same <a href="http://www.avritek.com/logistics-removal-recycling.html" target="_blank">electronic recycling services</a> we have always offered our clients, our services have evolved to be even more focused on ITAM (IT Asset Management) services, such as,<a href="http://www.avritek.com/data_product_destruction_and_sanitization.html" target="_blank"> IP &amp; Data Destruction</a>, <a href="http://www.avritek.com/IT-asset-value-recovery.html" target="_blank">IT Remarketing</a>, and <a href="http://www.avritek.com/logistics-removal-recycling.html" target="_blank">Reverse Logistics.</a></div>
<div></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div>I started this business over 11 years ago out of a single car garage.  Many garages and warehouses later, the core of what we do today is no different than what I did back then &#8211; maximizing the value of excess and obsolete equipment while providing exceptional customer service.</div>
<div></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div>I wanted to take a quick moment here to thank all of our clients (both past and present).  We truly would not be where we are today without the loyalty that so many of you have shown us.  I hope to think that our service and performance has something to do with that as well.</div>
<div></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div>I also wanted to take the opportunity to thank one individual in particular, Stu Wood our Business Development Manager.  Stu has put in a tremendous amount of time and effort in order for us to make this transition a success.  He deserves much of the credit in bringing about this change and his contribution in this process has been invaluable.</div>
<div></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div>Lastly, I encourage you to come join us at the <a href="http://sdcloudcomputing.com/" target="_blank">7th Annual Cloud Computing Conference this <span class="aBn" data-term="goog_1107778729"><span class="aQJ">Thursday, October 29th</span></span> </a>at the Mission Valley Town and Country.  We are a sponsor of the event and will have a booth for you to come by and say hello.</div>
<div></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div>Thank you once again for all of your continued support,</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div><strong><img class="CToWUd" src="https://ci6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/F36VvH90esJt6hi7M91OEHVq3kmR-9DZmNKYXxlTRevSXyTtBAC15yKY6l2pQ_LLwbdxiK5f6kSnd_dyyYoyDSjGdHpB44P366jfZkLCcwpmbfGs_Erzxl1pez12kiKrfldveYaN6-aFC4Z2rtkHyG0CQuiQKft4c9zjBc0=s0-d-e1-ft#https://gallery.mailchimp.com/3cff8a9d4df9dde6a8dd81831/images/df5d4e4f-57b5-40c1-bfcb-ddae57b26a94.png" alt="" width="200" height="21" align="none" /></strong></div>
<div>
<p><strong>Ed Pletner</strong></p>
<p>Chief Executive Officer</p>
</div>
<div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div><img class="CToWUd" src="https://ci5.googleusercontent.com/proxy/5h4s0Bne9gvEpWHcJtFepwz2Wz7k1qFytctoNQrSdVpB9AcfSZZcI6yCMe7usTBK6-AdF7h1BXpbF7z9qSqsKW-FDiNldpgNfAZ3DomapCYXzX1IXTs1Ew-w4-K6_sgIWhXgTDzCop8L3lYLpeZz5BsaHT0gcs1nLGkQIs4=s0-d-e1-ft#https://gallery.mailchimp.com/3cff8a9d4df9dde6a8dd81831/images/69ed9c52-0435-441e-aed9-dfb9bd76ea40.jpg" alt="" width="120" height="145" align="none" /></div>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://blog.avritek.com/2015/10/28/avr-recycling-is-now-avritek/">AVR Recycling is now Avritek!</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://blog.avritek.com">Avritek Blog | Secure Technology Asset Solutions</a>.</p>
]]></content>
